  "title": "remove `is_v=` from URL",
  "body": "We thought in early v1, it would be great to have that to make URL easy to upgrade. After two years, we haven't a usage for it and it's cryptic. I propose to remove it.\r\n\r\nSince nothing relies on it, it shouldn't be a breaking change.\r\n\r\nThoughts?",
